verbose_text: [XREF_BIBR] Additional experiments in rats have demonstrated that a VED may act through antihypoxic, antiapoptotic, and antifibrotic mechanisms, with effects that include decreased expression of hypoxia inducible factor-1 h, transforming growth factor-beta1 and apoptotic indices, enhanced smooth muscle / collagen ratio and preserved alpha-smooth muscle actin, and endothelial NO synthase expression.
